es de terrain et témoignages directs de victimes résistantes, cette réflexion transdisciplinaire propose un filet de sens pour appréhender l’horreur.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aDisappeared personszArgentina. 0aDisappeared persons--Social aspects--Argentina. 0aPolitical kidnappingzArgentinaxHistoryy20th century. 0aState crimeszArgentinaxHistoryy20th century. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2013z978311127412608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2013z978311127715840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276371858340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763718583423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763718583/original  a978-3-11-127412-6  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2013b2013  a978-3-11-127715-8  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2013b2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles